    "17306101": {
      "title": "Physical activity and public health in older adults: recommendation from the american college of sports medicine and the american heart association",
      "abstract": "ABSTRACTObjective:To issue a recommendation on the types and amounts of physical activity needed to improve and maintain health in older adults.Participants:A panel of scientists with expertise in public health, behavioral science, epidemiology, exercise science, medicine, and gerontology.Evidence:T"
